有機ko人/撐到最後贏分<br />\n<br />\n所以猜測係無謂，想分勝負重賽係唯一方法</blockquote><br />\n曹生出名冇重拳 哩個磅嚟講太高<br />\n講多無謂 重賽啦屌"},{"pid":"5e2c95ba3fdcf763dada092f3fb1c1079ec72a2a","tid":428021,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/體育/20962/-拳王出戰-曹星如贏定輸-五大拳擊評分準則\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F20962%2F-%E6%8B%B3%E7%8E%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%82%E8%B4%8F%E5%AE%9A%E8%BC%B8-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%BA%96%E5%89%87&d=TtaPMzyvtoMN0LA7bR7BlsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=00dc0781\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/體育/20962/-拳王出戰-曹星如贏定輸-五大拳擊評分準則</a></blockquote><br />\nhk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd50b5dedaadc5634afa85e7a22a81409dcb838","tid":428021,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"樓主係呢兩日最中立既評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bac541c88b4bcf0750b648a5dd8f5742b9c2cd","tid":428021,"uid":81399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9 佢頭腫主因唔係比人撞 <br />\n而係比人打左好撚多下導致</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句野擺明係<br />\nOn9: 佢頭腫主因唔係比人撞 <br />\n而係比人打左好撚多下導致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af13ae1a7bd46ff43461990d850175e1f1bab46","tid":428021,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都好，擺到明場拳係有得打，當曹星如冇眼腫，場拳邊個贏冇人敢寫包單，而事實我都睇到單計中頭應該真係曹星如多啲，但打拳既野我唔熟所以唔夠膽講邊個實際佔上風，因為曹星如有冇眼腫都應該會打得幾辛苦下，當然對方都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係想講一場五五拳，因為其中一方頭鎚意外令對手戰力下降(唔好話冇，個瘤真係見到都驚)，咁既情況下當判左河野贏，你地覺得反而係100%公平？相反曹星如唔好彩比人頭鎚完仲同人博到咁耐叫做馬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論：呢場真係super打和可能更好(論君子之爭)，但曹星如咁啱受惠左拳則而免除要博落去既風險，叫運氣，但真心唔覺同做馬扯得上關係。<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係乜愛港熱血撚，曹星如輸我都冇所謂，志外睇下人打下交姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nas a 香港人，我都支持佢重賽，打多次<br />\n不過唔會好似班連登仔咁，唔識拳例又9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8409d3d4ef7687dd4a17693e883765ba9d06170","tid":428021,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/體育/20962/-拳王出戰-曹星如贏定輸-五大拳擊評分準則\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F20962%2F-%E6%8B%B3%E7%8E%8B%E5%87%BA%E6%88%B0-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%82%E8%B4%8F%E5%AE%9A%E8%BC%B8-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%B3%E6%93%8A%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86%E6%BA%96%E5%89%87&d=TtaPMzyvtoMN0LA7bR7BlsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=00dc0781\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/體育/20962/-拳王出戰-曹星如贏定輸-五大拳擊評分準則</a></blockquote><br />\nhk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d722159942330512f9cb4dade9659c2abcec41","tid":428021,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15b8a3b90cf4db75e9ec9d5ed4d7d78f4f089c06","tid":428021,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"醫生咪又係我地既人，黎得我地主場出擊，仲會比你走咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28061622e122c87b92df572c0343acc7a0e2eb10","tid":428021,"uid":45147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生咪又係我地既人，黎得我地主場出擊，仲會比你走咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫生我相信有一定客觀準則既，的而且確話唔打得既時侯曹星如已經得翻一隻眼睇到野咁濟，我覺得玩到咁癲嗌停係合理既，因為唔停河野都係會專攻你傷口，到時搞到大獲冇乜意思<br />\n<br />